                        <a href="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/2014/09/fox-host-tells-ben-carson-you-as-president-is-like-a-lawmaker-doing-brain-surgery/" title="Fox host tells Ben Carson: You as president is like a lawmaker doing brain surgery" class="rpc-post-title" target="_self">Fox host tells Ben Carson: You as president is like a lawmaker doing brain surgery</a>
